lead_paragraph: John Terry's illustrious Chelsea career appears set to end on the sidelines after the captain was red carded in Saturday's loss to Sunderland and midfielder Nemanja Matic was one of the first of his team mates to pay tribute to the departing legend.

headline.print_headline: Matic Lauds Terry After Red Card Set to End Chelsea Career
headline.main: Matic Lauds Terry After Red Card Set to End Chelsea Career
